##################################################
# RoleSMP V2 -- main.sk
##################################################
# This is a documentation/entry-point file only.
# Skript auto-loads every .sk file under scripts/
# (including subfolders), so there is no explicit
# "import" step -- just make sure all files below
# are present in your scripts/ folder:
#
# scripts/
#  +- main.sk                (this file)
#  +- core/
#  |   +- setup.sk            global options + startup init
#  |   +- data.sk             variable layout documentation
#  |   +- recipes.sk          Role Ascension Scroll recipe + use
#  +- systems/
#  |   +- roles.sk            role assignment, reset, join, passive stat effects
#  |   +- cooldowns.sk        cooldown/charge cleanup on death+quit, stun lock
#  +- features/
#  |   +- abilities.sk        active role abilities (Farmer/Miner/Scout/Warrior/Archer)
#  |   +- combat.sk           damage interactions (Archer dmg halving, fire/poison arrows)
#  |   +- leveling.sk         level cost curve + /upgrade logic
#  +- gui/
#  |   +- rolemenu.sk         role-select GUI
#  |   +- levelgui.sk         per-role level chart GUI
#  +- commands/
#      +- player.sk           /roles, /upgrade, tab completion, help text
#      +- admin.sk            /resetcooldowns, /deletelock, /setrolelevel
#
# NOTE ON {prefix}: vanilla Skript "options:" blocks are
# local to the file they're declared in, so they can't be
# shared across split files. This split replaces {prefix}
# with the persistent variable {prefix}, set once in
# core/setup.sk on load.
